msgctxt "1396"
msgid "Financially Troubled Man"
msgstr "Hombre con problemas financieros"

msgctxt "1400"
msgid "Akiyama"
msgstr "Akiyama"

msgctxt "84_Financially Troubled Man"
msgid "I appreciate you telling me about him, but is this Shiobara\\r\n"
"guy really all that?"
msgstr "Agradezco que me hayas contado sobre él,\\r\n"
"pero ¿realmente es tan bueno ese tal Shiobara?"

msgctxt "96_Financially Troubled Man"
msgid "I mean, I'm outside his building now, and he, like, dragged\\r\n"
"this guy in..."
msgstr "Quiero decir, estoy afuera de su oficina ahora mismo\\r\n"
"y lo vi arrastrando a un tipo hacia el interior..."

msgctxt "108_Financially Troubled Man"
msgid "Sure, he looks nice enough, and he's been all, \"Just leave\\r\n"
"it to me!\" about everything..."
msgstr "Aunque parecía bastante amable, se la pasó repitiendo:\\r\n"
"\"¡Déjalo todo en mis manos!\"..."

msgctxt "120_Financially Troubled Man"
msgid "But seeing that guy getting pulled into his office makes me\\r\n"
"a little uneasy, if I'm being perfectly honest..."
msgstr "Pero ver a un tipo siendo arrastrado frente a mí me pareció\\r\n"
"algo inquietante, como si se estuviese ocultando algo..."

msgctxt "132_Financially Troubled Man"
msgid "I hate to be a pain, but do you happen to know any other moneylenders in the area?"
msgstr "Odio molestar, pero ¿podrías recomendarme otro prestamista de la zona?"

msgctxt "144_Akiyama"
msgid "This is definitely the place..."
msgstr "Este definitivamente es el lugar..."

